  "texts": [
    "core to the project of maintaining and building accountability, legitimacy, and trust.",
    "99 This statement underscores the vital role that transparency and the accessibility of reasons play in shaping the public's perception of the legitimacy of legal authorities and their decisions.",
    "The legitimation potential of transparency and accessibility operates on both the systemic level and the level of individual decisions.",
    "At the systemic level, understanding the structure of the system, the limits of its power, and its adherence to rules and accountability can confer legitimacy to the institution.",
    "100 Similarly, comprehending the specific reasons behind a bureaucratic decision can legitimize that individual decision."
  ]
